"     <div class=\"reference\">",
"      Hurst LC, Badalamente MA, Hentz VR, et al, &ldquo;Injectable Collagenase Clostridium Histolyticum for Dupuytren&rsquo;s Contracture,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       N Engl J Med",
"      </i>",
"      , 2009 361(10):968-79.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
